text.string: Assumptions: A Student Report can only be generated if that student is/was enrolled in at least 1 course. An instructor cannot be a student and a student cannot be an instructor Location status indicates whether location is in repair and whether it is available/not being used A bike can be assigned to multiple courses A Bike may or may not belong to a course (it could be new, in repair) Bike type indicates either street or dirt. Street bikes only can be assigned to street courses, and dirt bikes only assigned to dirt courses. Session can be either AM or PM
